25|$|In 2005, {{thousands}} of anti-nuclear demonstrators marched {{to commemorate the}} 1986 Chernobyl disaster and demand an end to government plans <b>to</b> <b>build</b> <b>a</b> <b>nuclear</b> plant in western France.|$|E
