25|$|In November 2011 Gulf Power {{stated that}} by the end of 2012 it hopes to finish buying off 4000 acres of land north of Pensacola, Florida in order <b>to</b> <b>build</b> <b>a</b> {{possible}} <b>nuclear</b> power station.|$|R
